></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><span style="color: inherit;">3. Choose breathable fabrics</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><span style="color: inherit;">4. Don't let sweat build up</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><span style="color: inherit;">5. Hygiene is key to keeping Fungal Acne at bay</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><span style="color: inherit;"><br></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><span style="color: inherit;">Remember, it's all about understanding your skin and giving it the care it needs!</span></span></p><p><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1679404125871" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1679404125871" data-layout-lg="12" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1679404125838" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1679404125838"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 25px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664p