="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1679404125865"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">Whether you're struggling to find the right fungal acne safe products or wondering what ingredients to avoid, we hope this blog can serve as a guide to help you whenever you're feeling a little lost.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">And whenever you might feel confused about products or have questions, the KS team is always here to help.</span></p><p><br></p><p>Take care and until next time.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Love, Brittney</p><p><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1688134559613" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1688134559613" data-layout-lg="3+9" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="3+9" data-layout-sm="3+9" data-layout-xs="12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-3 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653641854829" data-id="1653641854829"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1688134559565" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1688134559565" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-md" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/a33694dd-66a1-4edf-b1d8-175365a9cc6d/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/profile-brittnet.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="80%" data-height="auto" title="" width="768" height="768" natural-width="768" natural-height="768"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-9 gf_col-md-9 gf_col-sm-9 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653641924038" data-id="1653641924038"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1688134559526" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1688134559526"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">About Brittney</h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1688134559592" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1688134559592"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>Hi, SkinTalk readers! I'm Brittney and I’m 23 years old.&nbsp;<span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">I am a passionate and dedicated graduate cosmetologist.</span></p><p>Skincare has always captivated my interest, and <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 224, 237);">I find immense pleasure in helping others enhance their skin's health and appearance</span>.</p><p><br></p><p>Having struggled with acne-prone skin myself. However, my journey took a positive turn when I discovered Korean skincare. The transformative effects it had on my skin <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 224, 237);">brought back my confidence and self-assurance</span>.&nbsp;<span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">This personal experience inspired me to delve deeper into the world of Korean skincare.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p>Skincare is not just about superficial beauty; it's about nurturing and caring for yourself. By guiding you towards effective skincare routines and suitable products, we can not only enhance your skin's health but also boost your self-esteem.&nbsp;<span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">I am committed to <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 224, 237);">sharing my knowledge and expertise</span>.</span></p><p><br></p><p>Join me on this journey of self-care and discovery, where we unlock the secrets to beautiful and resilient skin. Remember, your skin deserves the best. With the right guidance and products, we can unleash its true potential.</p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 224, 237);"><br></span></p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 224, 237);">Together we can achieve healthy, glowing skin that radiates confidence and self-love!</span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1688651320176" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1688651320176" data-layout-lg="3+9" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="3+9" data-layout-sm="3+9" data-layout-xs="12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-3 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653641854829" data-id="1653641854829"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1688651320147" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1688651320147" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/a33694dd-66a1-4edf-b1d8-175365a9cc6d/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/profile-brittnet.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="80%" data-height="auto" title="" width="768" height="768" natural-width="768" natural-height="768"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-9 gf_col-md-9 gf_col-sm-9 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653641924038" data-id="1653641924038"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1688651320136" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1688651320136"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">About</h1><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Brittney</h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1688651320153" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1688651320153"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>Hi, SkinTalk readers! I'm Brittney and I’m 23 years old.&nbsp;<span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">I am a passionate and dedicated graduate cosmetologist.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">Skincare has always captivated my interest, and </span><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 224, 237);">I find immense pleasure in helping others enhance their skin's health and appearance</span><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">.</span></p><p><br></p><p>Having struggled with acne-prone skin myself. However, my journey took a positive turn when I discovered Korean skincare. The transformative effects it had on my skin <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 224, 237);">brought back my confidence and self-assurance</span>.&nbsp;<span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">This personal experience inspired me to delve deeper into the world of Korean skincare.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p>Skincare is not just about superficial beauty; it's about nurturing and caring for yourself. By guiding you towards effective skincare routines and suitable products, we can not only enhance your skin's health but also boost your self-esteem.&nbsp;<span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">I am committed to <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 224, 237);">sharing my knowledge and expertise</span>.</span></p><p><br></p><p>Join me on this journey of self-care and discovery, where we unlock the secrets to beautiful and resilient skin. Remember, your skin deserves the best. With the right guidance and products, we can unleash its true potential.</p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 224, 237);"><br></span></p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 224, 237);">Together we can achieve healthy, glowing skin that radiates confidence and self-love!</span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1682427936385" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1682427936385"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-xs" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr